abstract: Nebraska running back Ameer Abdulla is named Most Valuable Player in Senior Bowl; other college football news noted.
lead_paragraph: Abdullah of Nebraska rushed for 73 yards and added 40 receiving yards as he led the North to a 34-13 victory over the South in the Senior Bowl in Mobile, Ala.

headline.main: Abdullah Leads North in Senior Bowl
